description: Bangladesh's T20 World Cup defeat to South Africa in New York was marred by an umpiring error and a controversial Decision Review System rule. The leg-bye boundary was not added.

description: At one point, the match seemed to be slipping away from India. Akmal expressed his sincere regret on social media.
